verbose_text: To determine whether porphyra-334 inhibited MMP expression induced by UVA irradiation, human skin fibroblasts were irradiated with UVA (10 J/cm 2) and treated with porphyra-334 for 24 h. Based on RT-PCR, UVA irradiation significantly increased MMP-1 mRNA expression in culture medium (XREF_FIG).
